  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of the present study is to evaluate the effectiveness of two different delivery
      formats for weight management in a managed care setting. Mail-based weight counseling and
      phone-based weight counseling will be compared to each other and a control condition.
      Primary outcomes are participation rates in programs, weight change, and cost.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
